{"tid":1396333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工黨：已收集兩萬聯署 要求取消何君堯太平紳士資格","createTime":"2019-08-02T05:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:30:58.000Z","uid":212626,"like":114,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e75f9ea2d9cc430e811a73ac0af1f145a029be4b","tid":1396333,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"工黨多名成員到政府總部外抗議，表示在過去一周收集到超過兩萬名市民聯署，要求取消立法會議員何君堯太平紳士及鄉議局當然議員資格。政務司司長辦公室派人接收聯署信。<br />\n<br />\n工黨主席郭永健認為，有表面證據指何君堯與元朗襲擊事件中的白衣人施襲者，有不尋常關係，涉嫌鼓吹、教唆及指使黑社會使用暴力，令人質疑何君堯是否仍有資格擔任太平紳士。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，在收集聯署的過程中，亦有新界原居民反映，何君堯部分言論並不代表新界人的立場。<br />\n<br />\n聯署聲明指出，根據太平紳士條例，行政長官經顧及公眾利益及有關個案的一切其他情況後，可取消太平紳士資格。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2208591/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2208591%2F&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=98339eed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2208591/</a>"},{"pid":"350f3e130de56ecd4c71dfdfa0f66944938cf5fa","tid":1396333,"uid":87498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScOy5PzIYwccbAbb6Orpx3DSv9HCmZbn8huTPZdu08iued1gg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScOy5PzIYwccbAbb6Orpx3DSv9HCmZbn8huTPZdu08iued1gg%2Fviewform&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=394b90a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScOy5PzIYwccbAbb6Orpx3DSv9HCmZbn8huTPZdu08iued1gg/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"ea8d75802e1a638e09974bdf316390c7c21f6c12","tid":1396333,"uid":126256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:17:19.000Z","msg":"得兩萬咁少？<br />\n定係又係毅進制數學？？"},{"pid":"2cc23093b0c33c784890d78e305d1931a85c3688","tid":1396333,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:18:4